textAfterTable: 2 in Ukraine Innovation award Nominee: 2x Winner: 1x   Detailed description   Download .zip .tar.gz   Install with Composer   This class can be used to register events in Google calendar. It accesses the Google Calendar site authenticating as a given user. For now the class can only register a new event in the Google Calendar user, giving the event title, description, location, start and ending day and time.
